</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-21_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-22_ pf-text-1"><strong>Rapid response </strong>- According to research, over 40% of parents lack the basic first aid skills that could save their children's lives, indicating a significant gap in first aid knowledge that schools can help address.



























</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-24_ pf-text-1"><strong>Preparedness </strong>- Reports state that timely first aid intervention can double the chances of survival in certain emergencies, highlighting the need for trained school personnel.


























