</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-59_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-60_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-61_ pf-heading-1-h3">Why first aid training is indispensable in schools
</h3><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-63_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">First aid training empowers teachers and staff to act confidently and efficiently in a crisis, potentially saving lives. It also instils a sense of responsibility and readiness among the students, creating a safer school environment.















